var limit_width  = 700;
var limit_height = 200;

	zoneid_selected = zoneid_mobile;
}

</script></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">function setInOutAnimation(t){t.style.setProperty("-webkit-transition","all "+window.animationTime+"ms cubic-bezier(0.455, 0.030, 0.515,     var glb_realtime_map = {
        site: 'globoesporte',
        categories: ['home'],
        url: 'http://globoesporte.globo.com/tenis/'
    };

    var realtime = function(realtimeLoaded, msg){
        if(realtimeLoaded){
            return;
        }

        $.getScript('http://s.glbimg.com/bu/rt/js/glb-rt.js', function(){
            $.ajax({
                dataType: 'jsonp',
                
                url: 'http://s.glbimg.com/es/ge/static/live/globoesporte/json/globoesporte-home-agregador.js',
                
                jsonpCallback: 'glbrealtime_callback',
                cache: true,
                success: function(json){
                    $.glbrealtime({
                        data: json,
                        debug: false
                    });
                }
            });
        });
    }

    var realtimeLoaded = false;

    $(window).on('load', function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "onLoad");
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    })

    setTimeout(function(){
        realtime(realtimeLoaded, "timeout")
        realtimeLoaded = true;
    }, 3000);

</script><link rel="stylesheet"

  <script>
    var onImageLoad = function(event) {
      if (!window.pwtTempStorage) {
        window.pwtTempStorage = {};
      }

      var tgt = event.target;
      var dataImagePrefix = 'data:image';
      if (tgt.tagName === 'IMG' && tgt.parentElement && tgt.parentElement.dataset &&
        tgt.parentElement.dataset.pwt === 'true') {
        var key = tgt.src && tgt.src.substr(0, dataImagePrefix.length) === dataImagePrefix ?
          tgt.src : tgt.src.split('/').pop();
        if (!window.pwtTempStorage[key]) {
          window.pwtTempStorage[key] = {
            time: window.performance.now(),
            visibility: window.getComputedStyle(tgt).visibility,
          };
        }
      }
    }

    var calculateNumOfServerRenderedPinImages = function(event) {
      window.numOfServerRenderedPinImages = document.querySelectorAll('[data-pwt]').length;
    }

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", calculateNumOfServerRenderedPinImages);
    document.body.addEventListener('load', onImageLoad, true);

    window.addEventListener('load', function() {
      document.body.removeEventListener('load', onImageLoad, true);
      document.removeEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', calculateNumOfServerRenderedPinImages);
    });
  </script>
